    "(3) A researcher at an academic institution develops a application to collect data from (formerly) users.",
    "The application collects data from those who have agreed to 's terms of service enabling sharing of personal information with third-parties.",
    "Their profile picture, self-reported description, engagements on the platform, such as lists of who they 'like' or 'follow', and the political opinions they have published in their tweets, are harvested.",
    "Generative AI tools are used to extract survey-like information from each individual profile.",
    "These structured versions of the scraped data are then used to make granular-level predictions for population cells."
  ],
